<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id56b2238b-2930-11f1-a4c1-c531e6569a02" identifier="/us/usc/t14/s1921"><num value="1921">§ 1921.</num><heading> Corps of Cadets authorized strength</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The number of cadets appointed annually to the Academy shall be as determined by the Secretary but the number appointed in any one year shall not exceed six hundred.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id56b2238c-2930-11f1-a4c1-c531e6569a02">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/115/282/tI/s110/c/1/B">Pub. L. 115–282, title I, § 110(c)(1)(B)</ref>, <date date="2018-12-04">Dec. 4, 2018</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/132/4213">132 Stat. 4213</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
